title: Ep 35 - The Phrase to Change Your Life
itunes:title: Ep 35 - The Phrase to Change Your Life
description:
"Can't change it" That is a phrase that can change your life. So often we let things out of our control stress us out. In this episode we talk about that phrase and how it helps us take control of our life and relax, even when times get stressful.
